<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>三峡船闸输水廊道断面尺寸多目标优化分析网页模拟器</title>
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#f4f7fb;
    --card:#ffffff;
    --text:#111827;
    --muted:#667085;
    --line:#d9e1ec;
    --blue:#2563eb;
    --green:#0f766e;
    --orange:#b45309;
    --purple:#7c3aed;
    --red:#dc2626;
    --amber:#d97706;
    --ok:#15803d;
    --shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
    --radius:18px;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI","Microsoft YaHei",Arial,sans-serif;
    color:var(--text);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(37,99,235,.14), transparent 340px),
      linear-gradient(180deg,#eef5ff 0%,var(--bg) 330px);
  }
  header{
    max-width:1520px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:30px 32px 18px;
  }
  h1{
    margin:0;
    font-size:30px;
    line-height:1.25;
    letter-spacing:.1px;
  }
  .subtitle{
    margin:12px 0 0;
    max-width:1180px;
    color:var(--muted);
    line-height:1.75;
    font-size:15px;
  }
  main{
    max-width:1520px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:0 32px 38px;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:430px minmax(0,1fr);
    gap:20px;
  }
  .panel{
    background:var(--card);
    border:1px solid rgba(217,225,236,.95);
    border-radius:var(--radius);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .inputs{
    padding:18px;
    align-self:start;
    position:sticky;
    top:14px;
    max-height:calc(100vh - 28px);
    overflow:auto;
  }
  .section{
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top:16px;
    margin-top:16px;
  }
  .section:first-child{border-top:0;padding-top:0;margin-top:0}
  h2{font-size:18px;margin:0 0 12px}
  h3{font-size:15px;margin:0 0 12px;color:#1f2937}
  .hint{
    color:var(--muted);
    font-size:12px;
    line-height:1.58;
    margin:8px 0 0;
  }
  label{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 122px;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    margin:11px 0;
    font-size:13.5px;
  }
  label span{line-height:1.35;color:#263244}
  input[type=number]{
    width:100%;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:10px;
    padding:8px 9px;
    font-size:14px;
    outline:none;
    background:#fff;
  }
  input[type=number]:focus{
    border-color:#93c5fd;
    box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,.12);
  }
  .btns{display:flex;gap:9px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px}
  button{
    border:0;
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:10px 12px;
    font-weight:750;
    cursor:pointer;
    color:#111827;
    background:#e5e7eb;
  }
  button.primary{background:var(--blue);color:#fff}
  button.secondary{background:#e0f2fe;color:#075985}
  button:hover{filter:brightness(.985)}
  .dashboard{
    display:grid;
    gap:18px;
    min-width:0;
  }
  .model-banner{
    padding:16px 18px;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr auto;
    gap:16px;
    align-items:center;
  }
  .model-banner strong{font-size:16px}
  .model-banner p{
    margin:7px 0 0;
    color:var(--muted);
    line-height:1.65;
    font-size:13px;
  }
  .tag{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:8px 11px;
    background:#eef2ff;
    color:#3730a3;
    border:1px solid #c7d2fe;
    font-weight:800;
    white-space:nowrap;
    font-size:13px;
  }
  .kpis{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));
    gap:14px;
  }
  .kpi{
    padding:16px;
    background:#fff;
    border:1px solid rgba(217,225,236,.95);
    border-radius:var(--radius);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    min-width:0;
  }
  .name{
    color:var(--muted);
    font-size:13px;
    line-height:1.35;
  }
  .value{
    margin-top:8px;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:850;
    letter-spacing:-.25px;
    overflow-wrap:anywhere;
  }
  .sub{
    margin-top:6px;
    color:var(--muted);
    font-size:12px;
    line-height:1.5;
  }
  .chart-card{padding:18px}
  .chart-head{
    display:flex;
    align-items:flex-start;
    justify-content:space-between;
    gap:14px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .chart-head p{
    margin:4px 0 0;
    color:var(--muted);
    line-height:1.55;
    font-size:13px;
  }
  .legend{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px}
  .legend-item{display:inline-flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;white-space:nowrap}
  .swatch{width:18px;height:4px;border-radius:999px;background:#111}
  .total{background:var(--blue)} .con{background:var(--green)} .op{background:var(--orange)} .time{background:var(--purple)} .flow{background:#be123c} .vel{background:#111827}
  canvas{
    width:100%;
    height:440px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:15px;
    background:#fbfdff;
  }
  .grid2{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:18px;
  }
  .grid13{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1.08fr .92fr;
    gap:18px;
  }
  .card-pad{padding:18px}
  table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:collapse;
    font-size:13px;
    overflow:hidden;
    border-radius:12px;
  }
  th,td{
    padding:10px 9px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    text-align:left;
    vertical-align:top;
  }
  th{background:#f3f6fb;color:#374151;font-weight:850}
  tr:last-child td{border-bottom:0}
  .status{
    display:inline-flex;
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:5px 9px;
    font-size:12px;
    font-weight:850;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .status.ok{background:#dcfce7;color:var(--ok)}
  .status.warn{background:#fef3c7;color:#a16207}
  .status.bad{background:#fee2e2;color:#b91c1c}
  .formula{
    background:#f8fafc;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:14px;
    line-height:1.85;
    color:#263244;
    font-size:13px;
  }
  code{
    background:#eef2ff;
    color:#1e3a8a;
    padding:2px 6px;
    border-radius:7px;
    font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,"Liberation Mono","Courier New",monospace;
  }
  .formula-row{margin:2px 0}
  ul{
    margin:8px 0 0 19px;
    padding:0;
    color:#334155;
    font-size:13px;
    line-height:1.75;
  }
  .small-metrics{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));
    gap:10px;
    margin-top:12px;
  }
  .metric{
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    background:#fbfdff;
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:10px;
  }
  .metric .mname{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.35}
  .metric .mval{font-weight:850;margin-top:5px;font-size:15px}
  .note-box{
    background:#fff7ed;
    border:1px solid #fed7aa;
    color:#7c2d12;
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:12px 14px;
    font-size:13px;
    line-height:1.65;
    margin-top:12px;
  }
  @media(max-width:1180px){
    main{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .inputs{position:static;max-height:none}
    .kpis{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}
    .grid2,.grid13{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  }
  @media(max-width:720px){
    header,main{padding-left:16px;padding-right:16px}
    .kpis{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    label{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .model-banner{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .small-metrics{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    canvas{height:360px}
  }
  @media(max-width:480px){
    .small-metrics{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  }

  /* 计算过程响应动画 */
  .calc-overlay{
    position:fixed;
    inset:0;
    background:rgba(15,23,42,.28);
    backdrop-filter:blur(3px);
    z-index:999;
    display:none;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    padding:18px;
  }
  .calc-overlay.show{display:flex}
  .calc-box{
    width:min(520px,100%);
    background:#fff;
    border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,.95);
    border-radius:22px;
    box-shadow:0 24px 70px rgba(15,23,42,.22);
    padding:22px;
  }
  .calc-top{
    display:flex;
    gap:14px;
    align-items:center;
  }
  .spinner{
    width:42px;
    height:42px;
    border-radius:50%;
    border:4px solid #dbeafe;
    border-top-color:#2563eb;
    animation:spin .85s linear infinite;
    flex:0 0 auto;
  }
  @keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
  .calc-title{
    font-weight:850;
    font-size:18px;
  }
  .calc-desc{
    color:var(--muted);
    font-size:13px;
    margin-top:5px;
    line-height:1.55;
  }
  .calc-steps{
    display:grid;
    gap:8px;
    margin-top:18px;
  }
  .calc-step{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:9px;
    color:#64748b;
    font-size:13px;
  }
  .calc-dot{
    width:9px;
    height:9px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:#cbd5e1;
  }
  .calc-step.active{
    color:#1d4ed8;
    font-weight:750;
  }
  .calc-step.active .calc-dot{
    background:#2563eb;
    box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(37,99,235,.13);
  }
  .progress-wrap{
    margin-top:18px;
    height:10px;
    background:#e5e7eb;
    border-radius:999px;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .progress-bar{
    width:0%;
    height:100%;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#2563eb,#0f766e);
    border-radius:999px;
    transition:width .18s ease;
  }
  .calc-inline{
    display:none;
    align-items:center;
    gap:8px;
    color:#1d4ed8;
    font-weight:800;
    font-size:13px;
    background:#eff6ff;
    border:1px solid #bfdbfe;
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:7px 11px;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .calc-inline.show{display:inline-flex}
  .calc-inline.dirty{background:#fff7ed;border-color:#fed7aa;color:#9a3412}
  .mini-spinner{
    width:14px;
    height:14px;
    border-radius:50%;
    border:2px solid #bfdbfe;
    border-top-color:#2563eb;
    animation:spin .75s linear infinite;
  }


  /* 图表更新提示 */
  canvas.waiting-update{
    opacity:.72;
    filter:saturate(.75);
  }
  canvas.chart-updated{
    animation:chartFlash .9s ease;
  }
  @keyframes chartFlash{
    0%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(37,99,235,.0); border-color:#93c5fd}
    35%{box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(37,99,235,.20); border-color:#2563eb}
    100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(37,99,235,.0); border-color:var(--line)}
  }
  .update-toast{
    position:fixed;
    right:22px;
    bottom:22px;
    z-index:1000;
    display:none;
    background:#ecfdf5;
    color:#065f46;
    border:1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:10px 14px;
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight:850;
    box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(15,23,42,.13);
  }
  .update-toast.show{display:block;animation:toastInOut 1.5s ease both}
  @keyframes toastInOut{
    0%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}
    18%{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
    78%{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
    100%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="calc-overlay" id="calcOverlay" aria-live="polite" aria-label="模型正在计算">
  <div class="calc-box">
    <div class="calc-top">
      <div class="spinner"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="calc-title">模型正在重新计算</div>
        <div class="calc-desc" id="calcDesc">参数已更新，正在代入报告标定模型并刷新图表。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="calc-steps">
      <div class="calc-step active" id="step1"><span class="calc-dot"></span><span>读取参数并更新水力边界</span></div>
      <div class="calc-step" id="step2"><span class="calc-dot"></span><span>计算 A*、t(A)、Q(A)、v(A)</span></div>
      <div class="calc-step" id="step3"><span class="calc-dot"></span><span>校核时间、空间与流速约束</span></div>
      <div class="calc-step" id="step4"><span class="calc-dot"></span><span>刷新曲线、柱状图与对比表</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-wrap"><div class="progress-bar" id="calcProgress"></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<header>
  <h1>三峡船闸输水廊道断面尺寸多目标优化分析网页模拟器</h1>
  
  <p class="subtitle">
    本模拟器依据《三峡船闸输水廊道断面尺寸多目标优化分析》报告构建，用于展示廊道断面面积 A 对充泄水时间、
    输水流量、廊道流速、建设投资、运营延误损失及全生命周期总成本的影响。
    系统采用报告标定参数，并支持修改闸室尺寸、造价系数、运营损失系数和安全约束。
  </p>
  <p class="subtitle">
    默认基准值为：水力控制下限 A<sub>水力</sub>=68.91 m²，理论经济最优断面 A<sup>*</sup>=92.16 m²，
    开挖空间上限 A<sub>max</sub>=300 m²；对应总成本约为 62.82、62.19、73.71 亿元。
    当前版本中，L、B、H<sub>k</sub> 会联动更新 V、C<sub>t</sub>、K<sub>0</sub>、A<sup>*</sup> 与总成本。
    修改参数后，图表会进入“待更新”状态，按 Enter 或点击“重新计算”后刷新。
  </p>
</header>

<main>
  <aside class="panel inputs">
    <div class="section">
      <h2>报告标定参数</h2>
      <p class="hint">默认值已按报告第 4 章图表与第 4.3 节对比表标定，单位采用“亿元”和“m²”。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>一、闸室与水力边界</h3>
      <label><span>闸室长度 L（m）</span><input id="L" type="number" step="1" value="280"></label>
      <label><span>闸室宽度 B（m）</span><input id="B" type="number" step="0.1" value="34"></label>
      <label><span>槛上水深 H<sub>k</sub>（m）</span><input id="Hk" type="number" step="0.1" value="5"></label>
      <label><span>最大工作水头 ΔH（m）</span><input id="dH" type="number" step="0.1" value="45.2"></label>
      <label><span>最长输水时长 t<sub>max</sub>（min）</span><input id="tmax" type="number" step="0.1" value="13"></label>
      <label><span>水力下限 A<sub>min</sub>（m²）</span><input id="Amin" type="number" step="0.01" value="68.91"></label>
      <label><span>空间上限 A<sub>max</sub>（m²）</span><input id="Amax" type="number" step="1" value="300"></label>
      <p class="hint">输水时长采用报告曲线标定并与闸室体积联动：t(A)=C<sub>t</sub>/A，其中 C<sub>t</sub>=A<sub>min</sub>·t<sub>max</sub>·(V/V<sub>ref</sub>)。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>二、流量与流速标定</h3>
      <label><span>流量线性系数 q<sub>coef</sub><br><small>Q=qcoef·A</small></span><input id="qcoef" type="number" step="0.0001" value="1.2598"></label>
      <label><span>恒定输水总流量 Q<sub>v</sub>（m³/s）<br><small>v=Qv/A</small></span><input id="Qv" type="number" step="0.01" value="368.64"></label>
      <label><span>设计基准流速 v<sub>base</sub>（m/s）</span><input id="vbase" type="number" step="0.1" value="4"></label>
      <label><span>规范安全流速 v<sub>max</sub>（m/s）</span><input id="vmax" type="number" step="0.1" value="6"></label>
      <p class="hint">报告中 A-Q 图采用 Q 与 A 线性增长；A-v 图采用恒定输水总流量下 v 与 A 反比例递减。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>三、经济模型参数</h3>
      <label><span>单位面积造价 a（亿元/m²）</span><input id="a" type="number" step="0.001" value="0.08"></label>
      <label><span>固定投资 C<sub>fix</sub>（亿元）</span><input id="Cfix" type="number" step="0.01" value="47.45"></label>
      <label><span>运营损失综合常数 K<sub>0</sub>（亿元·m²）</span><input id="K0" type="number" step="0.01" value="679.48"></label>
      <p class="hint">建设成本 Ccon=a·A+Cfix；运营折现损失 Cop=K0/A；总成本 TC=Ccon+Cop。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>四、图表范围与导出</h3>
      <label><span>曲线起点 A<sub>plot,min</sub>（m²）</span><input id="AplotMin" type="number" step="1" value="40"></label>
      <label><span>曲线终点 A<sub>plot,max</sub>（m²）</span><input id="AplotMax" type="number" step="1" value="330"></label>
      <div class="btns">
        <button class="primary" id="calcBtn">重新计算</button>
        <button id="resetBtn">恢复报告默认值</button>
        <button id="csvBtn">导出 CSV</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <section class="dashboard">
    <div class="panel model-banner">
      <div>
        <strong>核心模型：TC(A)=aA+C<sub>fix</sub>+K<sub>0</sub>/A，A<sup>*</sup>=√(K<sub>0</sub>/a)</strong>
        <p>当理论 A<sup>*</sup> 位于 [A<sub>min</sub>, A<sub>max</sub>] 且满足流速安全约束时，推荐 A=A<sup>*</sup>；否则取约束边界。双侧对称廊道总面积为 A<sub>总</sub>=2A。</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:flex-end"><span class="tag">报告数据标定版 · 图表防重叠</span><span class="calc-inline" id="calcInline"><span class="mini-spinner"></span>正在计算</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="kpis">
      <div class="kpi">
        <div class="name">理论经济最优断面 A*</div>
        <div class="value" id="AstarOut">—</div>
        <div class="sub">由 √(K0/a) 自动计算。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div class="name">推荐实施断面 A</div>
        <div class="value" id="ArecOut">—</div>
        <div class="sub" id="recSub">综合时间、空间、流速约束。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div class="name">推荐方案充泄水时长</div>
        <div class="value" id="tOut">—</div>
        <div class="sub">报告最优断面约 9.7 min。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div class="name">推荐方案总成本现值</div>
        <div class="value" id="TCOut">—</div>
        <div class="sub">报告最优值约 62.19 亿元。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel card-pad">
      <h2>关键结果</h2>
      <div class="small-metrics">
        <div class="metric"><div class="mname">闸室有效水体容积 V</div><div class="mval" id="Vout">—</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="mname">时间常数 Ct</div><div class="mval" id="CtOut">—</div></div><div class="metric"><div class="mname">体积缩放系数 V/Vref</div><div class="mval" id="scaleOut">—</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="mname">推荐断面输水流量 Q</div><div class="mval" id="Qout">—</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="mname">推荐断面廊道流速 v</div><div class="mval" id="vOut">—</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="mname">一次性建设投资</div><div class="mval" id="CconOut">—</div></div>
