          <div class="formula-row">2. 闸室水体容积：<code>V=L×B×Hk=47600 m³</code>。</div>
          <div class="formula-row">3. 充泄水时长：<code>t(A)=Ct/A</code>，默认 Ct=68.91×13。</div>
          <div class="formula-row">4. 输水流量：<code>Q(A)=1.2598A</code>。</div>
          <div class="formula-row">5. 廊道流速：<code>v(A)=368.64/A</code>。</div>
          <div class="formula-row">6. 建设成本：<code>Ccon=0.08A+47.45</code>。</div>
          <div class="formula-row">7. 运营损失：<code>Cop=679.48/A</code>。</div>
